Title: Hide or Remove unlinked class
Describe: None
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
By default, all classes are displayed:

[UML]
@startuml
class C1
class C2
class C3
C1 -- C2
@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
But you can:
- `hide @unlinked` classes:

[UML]
@startuml
class C1
class C2
class C3
C1 -- C2

hide @unlinked
@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
- or `remove @unlinked` classes:

[UML]
@startuml
class C1
class C2
class C3
C1 -- C2

remove @unlinked
@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
